dataset.title: Taxonomy of Oncaeidae (Copepoda, Poecilostomatoida) from the Red Sea. V. Three species of Spinoncaea gen. nov. (ivlevi-group), with notes on zoogeographical distribution

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Böttger-Schnack, Ruth (2003): Taxonomy of Oncaeidae (Copepoda, Poecilostomatoida) from the Red Sea. V. Three species of Spinoncaea gen. nov. (ivlevi-group), with notes on zoogeographical distribution. Zoological Journal of the Linnean Society 137 (2): 187-226, DOI: 10.1046/j.1096-3642.2003.00056.x, URL: https://academic.oup.com/zoolinnean/article-lookup/doi/10.1046/j.1096-3642.2003.00056.x
